{"type":"message","id":"b322fca1","parentId":"5ff45a2b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:23:29.814Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The spark-ollama app exists on Modal! So the infrastructure is there. Now I need to understand what was built and what's missing. Let me check the workspace TOOLS.md for the current setup and understand what exists vs what needs to be built.\n\nThe session notes mentioned we were building:\n1. A complete Modal app that runs the full SPARK FastAPI on A100 with embedded Ollama\n2. A React-based SPARK UI (served from Modal static hosting)\n\nBut it seems like those files weren't saved to the workspace. Let me check if there's a clawd workspace that was referenced.","thinkingSignature":"0094b331850cbaaf50242c79074c3f1a55d5d0e11b4b2c1ba8c9c2401911139e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_pdyk6iz5kc8a_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-ChildItem C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\nova-gateway -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object Name"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":11576,"output":176,"cacheRead":13916,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25668,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774322601609}}
