{"type":"message","id":"23af9e97","parentId":"a518d79f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:26:28.677Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The curl is hanging. This might be because the FastAPI server is slow to start or the Ollama startup is blocking. Let me wait for it.\n\nActually, the health endpoint tries to start Ollama synchronously on first request. But `subprocess.Popen` with `run_in_executor` in an async context... let me think.\n\nActually, the issue might be that when I do `await loop.run_in_executor(None, _start_ollama_sync)`, the `_start_ollama_sync` function runs synchronously and includes:\n1. Starting Ollama subprocess\n2. Waiting up to 60 seconds for Ollama to come up\n3. Then pulling the model (which takes several minutes!)\n\n\nThis is blocking the async event loop, so the health check times out before Ollama even finishes starting. I should split the startup into two phases: first just launch the subprocess, then separately wait for it to be ready. And instead of pulling the model during the health check, I should pre-pull it beforehand.\n\nActually, the cleanest approach is to remove the model pull entirely from the health check and let it just report whether Ollama is running. The user can trigger the model pull separately when needed. But wait—the `_ollama_started[\"done\"]` flag starts as `False`, so the first health check will still try to start Ollama and block for that 60-second timeout before responding. I need to rethink this flow entirely.\n\nThe real issue is that Modal's sandboxed environment might not support GPU access properly, and Ollama's lazy initialization is happening synchronously on the first request. I should split this into two endpoints: one that just checks if Ollama is running, and another that handles the actual startup and model loading separately. Or better yet, use a background task to handle the initialization so the health endpoint isn't blocked by it.","thinkingSignature":"267f678063165c0f7f58c6ccb6bc49632335e19094f1798423eaa7011b5b8d85"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ybgxyozheub4_1","name":"process","arguments":{"action":"kill","sessionId":"tender-cloud"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":111492,"output":419,"cacheRead":13992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125903,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774326377154}}
