{"type":"message","id":"058b00ab","parentId":"166732c5","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:27:52.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still failing. The issue might be that `run_in_executor` with `None` as the executor is blocking. Actually, I think the issue is more fundamental - the `modal.asgi_app` decorator might not support module-level mutable state the way I'm using it. Also, in Modal's sandbox environment, the module might be imported fresh for each request.\n\nLet me try a completely different approach. Instead of trying to manage Ollama as a subprocess, let me check if there's a way to use Modal's native capabilities better.\n\nActually, I think the real issue is that in Modal's sandboxed environment, Ollama can't access the GPU properly. The \"Unable to detect NVIDIA/AMD GPU\" warning during install suggests CUDA isn't available to Ollama in the container.\n \nOllama might still run in CPU mode on Modal's A100, so let me verify if it's actually functioning. I could also try switching to `modal.web_endpoint` or a `BackgroundTask` that runs independently. But really, the approach of starting Ollama on each cold start is too slow - I need it running continuously instead. Looking at the deploy output, it seems to have succeeded quickly this time, which is interesting.\n\nThe image was cached from the previous build, so it didn't rebuild the dependencies. The mount just updated the Python file. But when the container starts fresh, it's running the new code with Ollama installed, yet the connection is still failing - which suggests either Ollama isn't starting properly, the port is blocked, or something else is preventing the server from responding.\n\nActually, I'm wondering if this is a Modal sandbox limitation - maybe Ollama's server can't bind to the port or the GPU drivers aren't available in the sandbox environment. Let me test with a simple health check to see if the container itself is even reachable.","thinkingSignature":"fcdec3bcfd689c21b65cbeb5faaf08a5ad2ffc469ae1574519c246b33b2ffe06"},{"type":"text","text":"Still failing. Let me check if the container is even reaching the web server:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kby2b6dypz8f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s --max-time 15 https://toxzak-svg--spark-ollama.modal.run/ 2>&1 | head -3","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":116268,"output":448,"cacheRead":13992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":130708,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774326460018}}
