{"type":"message","id":"22b56a6e","parentId":"9842908e","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:28:44.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach sent \"?\" which means he's waiting or confused about what's happening. Let me give him a clear, concise update.","thinkingSignature":"f54c2922eba64be67cf58907fb5a88059611c37218a4c1670b883626f64b0e4c"},{"type":"text","text":"\nThe subagent is still checking. The issue: when we `modal deploy`, the code runs in Modal's sandbox container. Ollama installs fine but can't find the GPU — Modal's A100s don't expose CUDA the way Ollama expects it.\n\nQuick fix path: instead of Ollama, use Modal's native model serving — they have a `modal.inference` API for running open models directly. That's a cleaner integration than fighting Ollama's GPU detection.\n\nWant me to switch to that approach?"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":130,"cacheRead":127773,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":127903,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774326518879}}
