{"type":"message","id":"84633eea","parentId":"7dd00473","timestamp":"2026-03-24T04:29:42.009Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`gpu` parameter is available for `Sandbox.create`! So I can create a GPU-enabled sandbox that runs Ollama, and then the web app (without GPU) can communicate with it via HTTP.\n\nThe architecture:\n1. `web_server` - ASGI app without GPU, handles HTTP requests\n2. `ollama_sandbox` - GPU-enabled sandbox running Ollama, started once at deploy time\n\nThe web server can talk to the sandbox via its internal IP or via a Modal network file system volume.\n\nWait, actually the cleanest approach might be:\n1. Use `Sandbox.create` with `gpu=\"A100\"` to create a sandbox\n\n\n2. Run Ollama inside the sandbox\n3. Have the ASGI app proxy requests to the sandbox\n\nBut Sandboxes are temporary and cost money while running. For a deployed web app, I'd need the sandbox running continuously. Let me reconsider — maybe I should just run the inference directly in the ASGI container using GPU passthrough instead.\n\nThe real issue was that Ollama's install script couldn't find the GPU, but if I explicitly request GPU access via `gpu=\"A100\"` in Modal and run Ollama directly, it should detect the GPU properly. Let me try adding the GPU parameter and starting Ollama as a subprocess within the containerized ASGI app itself.","thinkingSignature":"22de2176dbb26641715c5fdacdf2ce30604c7aa17b3129733c8c3028c8fa227c"},{"type":"text","text":"Found it — I was missing `gpu=\"A100\"` in the decorator. That's why Ollama couldn't find the GPU. Let me fix the deploy with explicit GPU allocation:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r9dn1336w5bx_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\workspace\\spark\\modal_spark.py","oldText":"@app.function(image=_image, timeout=3600, scaledown_window=600)\n@modal.asgi_app(label=\"spark-ollama\")\ndef api():\n    from fastapi import FastAPI\n    from fastapi.responses import HTMLResponse\n    import httpx\n\n    api = FastAPI()","newText":"@app.function(image=_image, timeout=3600, scaledown_window=600, gpu=\"A100\")\n@modal.asgi_app(label=\"spark-ollama\")\ndef api():\n    from fastapi import FastAPI\n    from fastapi.responses import HTMLResponse\n    import httpx\n\n    api = FastAPI()"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117098,"output":496,"cacheRead":13992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":131586,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774326568308}}
