{"type":"message","id":"3b500ef4","parentId":"6ddc3f6b","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:49:28.548Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zach is confirming the path. I've already read the notebook and given the analysis. Let me confirm and see if he wants me to make changes to the notebook.","thinkingSignature":"e3bab8ab0db64e62d47d07389d108845b4b5f3a81e47e1e352d0bc5484575719"},{"type":"text","text":"Already read it and gave you the full breakdown above. Want me to make the fixes directly to the notebook? The main changes I'd make:\n\n1. **Remove `detach()` on hidden state** — let router learn from task signal\n2. **Mix query-phase oracle into Phase 1** — teach router what READ/WRITE patterns look like during queries\n3. **Soft transition into Phase 2** — gradual reduction of oracle routing over first 500 steps\n4. **Minimum route density penalty** — auxiliary loss penalizing if non-SKIP route fraction drops below threshold"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43,"output":154,"cacheRead":13992,"cacheWrite":105155,"totalTokens":119344,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774331357842}}
