{"type":"message","id":"17da12d3","parentId":"cf100602","timestamp":"2026-03-24T05:58:55.476Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"All four fixes are in place. Let me now summarize for Zach.","thinkingSignature":"2f76b50b00db5f27b204d31994375af0be5b4beb3144f1aeaa57545837e67663"},{"type":"text","text":"All 4 fixes applied to the notebook. Here's what changed:\n\n**Fix #1 — Removed `detach()` on hidden state** (`ArchitectureB.forward`)\n- Before: `hfr = self._hidden.detach() if route_stop_grad else self._hidden`\n- After: `hfr = self._hidden` — router gets full task gradient always\n- This was the root cause: Phase 2 router learned nothing because all useful signal was cut off\n\n**Fix #2 — Added GRU to trainable params** (`SRMoETrainer.__init__`)\n- `self.params` now includes `model.gru.parameters()` so hidden state carries meaningful task signal\n\n**Fix #3 — Phase 2 gradual transition** (training cell)\n- First 300 imitation learning epochs use oracle routing, then learned routing phases in\n- Before: hard switch at ep 0 — model saw zero learned routing signal for 5000 epochs\n- After: smooth ramp from oracle → learned over 300 steps\n\n**Fix #4 — Density penalty** (`SRMoETrainer`)\n- Added `_density_loss()` — penalizes if non-SKIP fraction drops below 15%\n- Prevents the router from collapsing into \"always SKIP\"\n\n**Fix #5 — Mask encode-phase SKIP from route CE** (`SRMoETrainer`)\n- Route CE loss now ignores SKIP actions during encode phases\n- These aren't real routing decisions — they're just oracle artifacts during the delay period\n- Lets the router learn from query-phase READ patterns instead\n\nReady to re-run Phase 1 + Phase 2. Re-run Phase 1 first (fresh pretrain with fixes), then Phase 2."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":99002,"output":357,"cacheRead":13992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113351,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774331917691}}
